{
  "uid": "lengua-product",
  "title": "Lengua — Product",
  "description": "Are people learning and coming back? Daily reviews, cards created, signups, and active users from the server-side product metrics (task 5.2.5): reviews_total, cards_created_total, signups_total, active_users. The CEFR-distribution panel is pending a proficiency metric (see note + infra/grafana/README.md). The consent-gated PostHog funnel (5.9) is the authoritative product analytics. Select the Prometheus/Mimir data source via ${datasource}.",
  "tags": ["lengua", "product"],
  "editable": true,
  "timezone": "",
  "schemaVersion": 39,
  "version": 1,
  "refresh": "1m",
  "time": { "from": "now-7d", "to": "now" },
  "timepicker": {},
  "annotations": { "list": [] },
  "templating": {
    "list": [
      {
        "name": "datasource",
        "label": "Prometheus / Mimir data source",
        "type": "datasource",
        "query": "prometheus",
        "refresh": 1,
        "hide": 0,
        "current": {},
        "options": []
      }
    ]
  },
  "panels": [
    {
      "id": 1,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Reviews (24h)",
      "description": "Flashcards graded in the last 24h (reviews_total).",
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource}" },
      "gridPos": { "h": 6, "w": 6, "x": 0, "y": 0 },
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "unit": "short", "min": 0 }, "overrides": [] },
      "options": { "reduceOptions": { "calcs": ["lastNotNull"] }, "colorMode": "value", "graphMode": "area" },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource}" },
          "expr": "sum(increase(reviews_total[1d]))",
          "legendFormat": "reviews/day"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Cards created (24h)",
      "description": "Cards saved into decks in the last 24h (cards_created_total).",
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource}" },
      "gridPos": { "h": 6, "w": 6, "x": 6, "y": 0 },
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "unit": "short", "min": 0 }, "overrides": [] },
      "options": { "reduceOptions": { "calcs": ["lastNotNull"] }, "colorMode": "value", "graphMode": "area" },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource}" },
          "expr": "sum(increase(cards_created_total[1d]))",
          "legendFormat": "cards/day"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Signups (24h)",
      "description": "New users first seen in the last 24h (signups_total — a process-local proxy; PostHog 5.9.2 is authoritative).",
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource}" },
      "gridPos": { "h": 6, "w": 6, "x": 12, "y": 0 },
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "unit": "short", "min": 0 }, "overrides": [] },
      "options": { "reduceOptions": { "calcs": ["lastNotNull"] }, "colorMode": "value", "graphMode": "area" },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource}" },
          "expr": "sum(increase(signups_total[1d]))",
          "legendFormat": "signups/day"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Active users (now)",
      "description": "Distinct users active within the recent rolling window (active_users gauge). max() across instances.",
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource}" },
      "gridPos": { "h": 6, "w": 6, "x": 18, "y": 0 },
      "fieldConfig": { "defaults": { "unit": "short", "min": 0 }, "overrides": [] },
      "options": { "reduceOptions": { "calcs": ["lastNotNull"] }, "colorMode": "value", "graphMode": "area" },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource}" },
          "expr": "max(active_users)",
          "legendFormat": "active users"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Daily reviews & cards created",
      "description": "Engagement over time: review and card-creation rate.",
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource}" },
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 6 },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": { "unit": "short", "min": 0, "custom": { "drawStyle": "line", "fillOpacity": 10 } },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": { "legend": { "displayMode": "list", "placement": "bottom" }, "tooltip": { "mode": "multi" } },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource}" },
          "expr": "sum(rate(reviews_total[$__rate_interval]))",
          "legendFormat": "reviews/s"
        },
        {
          "refId": "B",
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource}" },
          "expr": "sum(rate(cards_created_total[$__rate_interval]))",
          "legendFormat": "cards/s"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 6,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Active users & signups over time",
      "description": "Active-user gauge (max across instances) and the signup rate.",
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource}" },
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 12, "y": 6 },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": { "unit": "short", "min": 0, "custom": { "drawStyle": "line", "fillOpacity": 10 } },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": { "legend": { "displayMode": "list", "placement": "bottom" }, "tooltip": { "mode": "multi" } },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource}" },
          "expr": "max(active_users)",
          "legendFormat": "active users"
        },
        {
          "refId": "B",
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource}" },
          "expr": "sum(rate(signups_total[$__rate_interval]))",
          "legendFormat": "signups/s"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 7,
      "type": "text",
      "title": "CEFR level distribution — pending a metric",
      "description": "Documented gap: no per-band CEFR metric is emitted yet.",
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 14 },
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "### CEFR level distribution — pending a metric\n\nThe backend does **not** yet emit a CEFR-band metric, so this panel is intentionally a placeholder (no PromQL target) rather than a broken query.\n\n**To light this panel up (Phase 6 follow-up):** add an observable gauge — e.g. `proficiency_cefr_band` labelled by `band` (A1…C2), derived from `lengua_core.proficiency` per active language — to `app/product_metrics.py`, then replace this text panel with a bar gauge / pie over `sum by (band) (proficiency_cefr_band)`.\n\nUntil then, CEFR distribution is observable directly in the database (`proficiency`/`languages`). Tracked in `planning/outstanding-work.md` §11."
      }
    }
  ]
}
